{"lastModified":1751536111780,"uri":"c::17951852342::vessel::0ffc6c30-37d8-11f0-b38b-bfe78b64443f","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nIris, our luxurious 2025 Lagoon 46 catamaran, is the ideal choice for your next unforgettable getaway. With 4 double cabins, each featuring its own ensuite bathroom, and 2 additional crew cabins, Iris can comfortably accommodate up to 8 guests+2 crew. Perfect for skippered charters and available for bareboat charters for highly experienced sailors, Iris offers a blend of comfort, performance, and style.\n\nThis modern catamaran is equipped with top-tier amenities, including air conditioning, a generator, a watermaker, and solar panels, ensuring a seamless experience at sea. Her sailing equipment features a classic mainsail, bimini, flybridge, and an outside GPS plotter, providing both comfort and navigational ease.\n\nStep onboard and enjoy a fully-equipped galley with a freezer, fridge, oven, cooker, and sink. Outside, an audio system and speakers enhance your relaxation on deck, making every moment onboard memorable.\n\nExperience the best of the sea aboard Iris, your gateway to the ultimate sailing adventure","blueprint":{"name":"IRIS","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::0ffc6c30-37d8-11f0-b38b-bfe78b64443f::assets::87ad1c40-37db-11f0-8592-13b9467decdc/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::0ffc6c30-37d8-11f0-b38b-bfe78b64443f::assets::87a3a660-37db-11f0-8592-13b9467decdc/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::0ffc6c30-37d8-11f0-b38b-bfe78b64443f::assets::87a1f8b0-37db-11f0-8591-13b9467decdc/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::0ffc6c30-37d8-11f0-b38b-bfe78b64443f::assets::87df76e0-37db-11f0-8592-13b9467decdc/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::0ffc6c30-37d8-11f0-b38b-bfe78b64443f::assets::87b46f40-37db-11f0-8592-13b9467decdc/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::0ffc6c30-37d8-11f0-b38b-bfe78b64443f::assets::87a2e310-37db-11f0-8